commit.message: Merge #464 (update supported API versions).

Update supported Graph API versions.

  - Remove deprecated version 2.10.
  - Add new version 5.0.
Merge #462 (add GraphAPIError subcodes).

Add subcodes to GraphAPIError.

Add `error_subcode` field to GraphAPIError objects if it exists.

Close #432. Close #453.

Co-authored-by: Martey Dodoo <martey@mobolic.com>
Merge #461 (improve automated testing).

Reorganize tests.

  - Reorganize automated tests into multiple files.
  - Rename test case objects to make it clearer than they inherit from
    FacebookTestCase.
  - Remove broken `test_request` test case.

Change test runner command.

Use "-m unittest discover" instead of manually calling the
`test_facebook` script. This allows us to use the entire `test`
directory.
Merge #460 (add support for API version 4.0).

Add support for API version 4.0.

Co-authored-by: Martey Dodoo <martey@mobolic.com>
Merge #458 (add application secret proof support).

Add support for application secret proofs.

  - Install mock package in CircleCI configuration when running tests in
    Python 2.
  - Abstract adding a parameter to post_args or args to reduce code
    duplication between adding access token and application secret
    proofs.

Co-authored-by: Travis Thieman <travis.thieman@gmail.com>
Co-authored-by: Christian Ledermann <christian.ledermann@gmail.com>
Co-authored-by: Dmytro Litvinov <Litvinov.Dmytro.IT@gmail.com>
Co-authored-by: Martey Dodoo <martey@mobolic.com>
Merge #456 (comment out malfunctioning test).

Comment out malfunctioning automated test.

Temporarily comment out `test_function_returns_correct_connections`
automated test.
Merge #455 (remove support for Graph API v2.9).

Remove support for Graph API version 2.9.

  - Remove support for Graph API version 2.9.
  - Change default Graph API version to 2.10.
  - Add missing changelog entry about removal of Graph API version 2.8.
